# Adding Vaccination Tracking with Email Notifications

Here's a concise implementation approach:

## 1. **Create Vaccination Entity**
```java
@Entity
@Table(name = "vaccinations")
public class Vaccination extends BaseEntity {
    @ManyToOne
    @JoinColumn(name = "pet_id")
    private Pet pet;

    private String vaccineName;

    @DateTimeFormat(pattern = "yyyy-MM-dd")
    private LocalDate vaccinationDate;

    @DateTimeFormat(pattern = "yyyy-MM-dd")
    private LocalDate nextDueDate;

    // getters/setters
}
```

## 2. **Update Pet Entity**
Add to `Pet.java`:
```java
@OneToMany(cascade = CascadeType.ALL, fetch = FetchType.EAGER, mappedBy = "pet")
@OrderBy("vaccinationDate ASC")
private final Set<Vaccination> vaccinations = new LinkedHashSet<>();

public void addVaccination(Vaccination vaccination) {
    vaccination.setPet(this);
    this.vaccinations.add(vaccination);
}
```

